<div id="about-the-community" class="section-spacer">
    <h2 class="sect-title">About Erlton</h2>
    <div class="col-grid-2">
        <div>
            <p class="par-lg">Established back in 1906, the community in Erlton exudes a definitive old world charm that attracts potential homebuyers and real estate investors alike. </p>
            <p class="par-lg">The community is bound by the Spiller Road on the east, the Mission Road on the south and the Elbow River on the west and north.</p>
            <p class="par-lg">Homes for sale in Erlton primarily comprise vintage townhomes and recently developed apartment condominiums. </p>
            <p class="par-lg">A typical residential unit within the community will be available for sale from around $500,000 up to $700,000.</p>
        </div>
